{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/blogs/cppbasic1/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Chenxiao's Blog","author":"Chenxiao Guan"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"d1923491-be6f-5672-9e0f-705580404907","excerpt":"这两天面了一波腾讯游戏部门的实习，被C++搞的死去活来，索性从头到尾学一波C++。这个语言我之前一直 觉得就只是一个升级版的C而已，面完这次试才发现好像完全不仅仅如此。这个系列从最基础的C++开始记起，希望自己能学到一些东西。 Hello World! 所以C++的hello world…","html":"<blockquote>\n<p>这两天面了一波腾讯游戏部门的实习，被C++搞的死去活来，索性从头到尾学一波C++。这个语言我之前一直 觉得就只是一个升级版的C而已，面完这次试才发现好像完全不仅仅如此。这个系列从最基础的C++开始记起，希望自己能学到一些东西。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"hello-world\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#hello-world\" aria-label=\"hello world permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Hello World!</h3>\n<p>所以C++的hello world程序是长成什么样子的？我们创建一个名为<code class=\"language-text\">hello</code>的文件夹，在内新建一个<code class=\"language-text\">.cpp</code>的文件\n命名为<code class=\"language-text\">helloworld.cpp</code>。然后在文件内输入：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cpp\"><pre class=\"language-cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"token macro property\">#<span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">&lt;iostream></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"token function\">main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    std<span class=\"token operator\">::</span>cout <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Hello World!\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;&lt;</span> std<span class=\"token operator\">::</span>endl<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// print hello world</span>\n    std<span class=\"token operator\">::</span>cin<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// get a standard input and terminate the program</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>打开terminal，输入</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">g++ helloworld.cpp -o helloworld <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> ./helloworld</code></pre></div>\n<p>在terminal中就会出现<code class=\"language-text\">Hello World!</code>,并在敲任意键后退出程序。</p>\n<h3 id=\"一些实用技巧\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9B%E5%AE%9E%E7%94%A8%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7\" aria-label=\"一些实用技巧 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>一些实用技巧</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cpp\"><pre class=\"language-cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"token function\">main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> i1 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">7.2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// i1 becomes 7</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> i2 <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token number\">7.2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//error: floating point to interger conversion</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> i3 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token number\">7.2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// same error as above, and the equal sign is redundent</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"difference-between-const-and-constexpr\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#difference-between-const-and-constexpr\" aria-label=\"difference between const and constexpr permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Difference between <code class=\"language-text\">const</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">constexpr</code></h4>","frontmatter":{"title":"C++基础篇01：Hello World!","date":"April 18, 2019","description":"被国内面试搞得我不知所措，无奈从头开始学C++。"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/cppbasic1/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/leetcode22/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"LeetCode 17 & 22: 两道Medium DFS題目"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/leetcode23/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"LeetCode 23: Merge k Sorted Lists"}}}}}